videoDetails.Title: How to Create Desmos Art 2  Curves, Waves, Ellipses  Step by Step Guide
videoDetails.Description:
If you enjoy playing around with functions and graphs, you might be interested in the famous Desmos Art. You can create a whole bunch of creative artworks like logos, patterns, pictures, cartoon characters and portraits by only using DESMOS Graphing Calculator. This is the second video of DESMOS ART Video Series. In this video, you can adding curves, waves and ellipses. I will record more videos about desmos and share all my experience soon.
